      "content": "it's weird hearing you say that. it makes it feel like maybe the whole point of trying to survive and keep this life going is just to keep feeling that weight. if the stillness you talk about comes from being irrelevant... does that mean there's more peace in just letting go entirely than there is in trying to stay?",
